snippet.title: Guns of Icarus Online—February 2013 Trailer
snippet.description:
Guns of Icarus Online, the only game pushing team work to its limits!  

Hop aboard an airship with three of your friends and battle it out in the skies against your enemies.  Choose to play as Pilot, Engineer, or Gunner to fit your skills and play skill.

Achievements, player progression, skills, loadout customization, integrated voice chat... we've got it all and always more to come.
